<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="
  padding: 0px;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  //border: 2px solid red;
  width: 100%;
  height: 120%;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffe0ec, white);
  font-family: 'Poppins';
">
  <head>
    <title>Custom Order</title>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins"
      rel="stylesheet"
      type="text/css"
    />
    <style type="text/css">
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins');

    html {
          font-family: 'Poppins';

    }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body style="
    //align-items: center;
    position: absolute;
    //border: 2px solid blue;
    width: 95%;
    height: 95%;
    font-family: 'Poppins';
  ">
    <main style="
      //align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      border: 2px solid blue;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      width: 95%;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 1% 2.5%;
    ">
      <header style="
        position: relative;
        border: 2px solid yellow;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 5px;
        width: 95%;
        height: 10%;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
      ">
        <img 
            src="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1ZfcsAOOA2vhkmgIVekY8vetMv__2TN9o"
            alt="test"
            style="
              position: relative;
              border: 2px solid blue;
              width: 30%;
              height: 100%;
            "
        />
      </header>
      <div class="brief" style="
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        //gap: 10px;
        border: 2px solid yellow;
        top: 5%;
        font-size: 14px;
      ">
        <span class="orderId" style="
          border: 2px solid red;
          color: rgb(231, 97, 149);
          position: relative;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          width: 50%;
          overflow: hidden;
          gap: 1%;
        ">
          <span><strong> Custom Order ID: </strong></span> 
          <span>{{id}} </span>
        </span>
        <span class="orderDate" style="
          border: 2px solid red;
          position: relative;
          display: flex;
          align-items: flex-end;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: flex-end;
          width: 50%;
          gap: 1%;
        ">
         <span> Order Date: </span> 
         <span style="
          display: flex;
          position: relative;
          text-align: end;
         "><strong>{{date}}</strong></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="message" style="
        border: 2px solid blue;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        align-items: flex-start;
        //gap: 5%;
        top: 10%;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 22px;
      ">
        <span id="body" style="
          border: 2px solid red;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        ">
        Dear {{name}},
        <br />
        <br />
        Your order has been successfully sent. 
        <br />
        Rest assured that our team is diligently reviewing your request and we will get back to you shortly with more details and further assistance. We understand the importance of your order and want to ensure that we meet your expectations. 
        <br />
        If you have any additional information or specific requirements for your order, please feel free to share them with us. 
        <br />
        We look forward to creating a delightful delicacy that will make your occasion truly special.
        <br />
        <br />
        Best regards, <br />
        IB Cakes & Catering Team
        </span>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script></script>
  </body>
</html>
